// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1780 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 9a121ab4-7738-512e-ae16-9d98743610fd

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
